dct_title_s: Pianta guida della città di Roma veduto a volo d'uccello
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Selected buildings and city walls shown pictorially. Oriented with north toward the lower right. Includes street index. Originally issued folded in cover 17 x 12 cm.
